                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000067cf630c-b34d-4fdb-96e3-39d4a481860d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∆\ ABC\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000167cf630c-b34d-4fdb-96e3-39d4a481860d"> </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000267cf630c-b34d-4fdb-96e3-39d4a481860d">Gi </span><span class="pt-00000267cf630c-b34d-4fdb-96e3-39d4a481860d">†</span><span class="pt-00000267cf630c-b34d-4fdb-96e3-39d4a481860d">&#182;&#206;dj</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000167cf630c-b34d-4fdb-96e3-39d4a481860d"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\frac{1}{2}\left| \begin{matrix}0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1\\3 &amp; -5 &amp; 1\\3 &amp; 3 &amp; 1\\\end{matrix}\right| \) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000067cf630c-b34d-4fdb-96e3-39d4a481860d {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000167cf630c-b34d-4fdb-96e3-39d4a481860d {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000267cf630c-b34d-4fdb-96e3-39d4a481860d {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000037c6b4e5-ab6a-4964-84f6-04df6aefd90b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=\frac{1}{2}\times \left(9+15\right)=\frac{1}{2}\times 24=12\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000137c6b4e5-ab6a-4964-84f6-04df6aefd90b"> </span><span class="pt-00000237c6b4e5-ab6a-4964-84f6-04df6aefd90b">eM&#169; GKK|</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000037c6b4e5-ab6a-4964-84f6-04df6aefd90b {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000137c6b4e5-ab6a-4964-84f6-04df6aefd90b {font-family: SolaimanLip